[Diary page 5]
type=message_box
version=2
text=_""<rt image=map:Lutius.png image-align=left><p font-size=24 text-align=left font-face=FreeSerif font-weight=bold font-color=2F9131>"
_"Diary of Lutius"
"</p><p line-spacing=3 font-size=12><br>"
_"Finally!<br>This island seems to be made for us, it is a present of the Gods to my people and me.<br>Until now, we have only seen a small part of this island, but this part is allready leading sunbeams to my mind, feeling as if we found an unpayable treasure, a land like paradise.<br>On this island, we will start our new life, we will build up an outpost for our exile, which perhaps will become a new, beautiful home to everyone of us."
"</p></rt>""
window_title=_A new islands
is_modal=true
