[Diary page 5.1]
type=message_box
version=2
text=_""<rt image=map:Lutius.png image-align=left><p font-size=24 text-align=left font-face=FreeSerif font-weight=bold font-color=2F9131>"
_"Diary of Lutius"
"</p><p line-spacing=3 font-size=12><br>"
_"As Saledus and I walked through these wonderful forests in the north, we felt that our new future had just begun. This land is so peaceful, nice and beautiful, I could stay here until the end of my life.<br>But until that day, a lot of years will hopefully go by. For now, we should concentrate on the present and build a few lumberjacks and a sawmill, to produce some good build-materials.<br>But we shouldn't forget to save this natural bounty. These forests should last forever, so we really should build up a forester too.<br><br>"
_"* Build up three lumberjacks, a forester and a sawmill."
"</p></rt>""
window_title=_The green forests
is_modal=true
width=450
height=350
button_00=OK

